        <content type="html" xml:base="https://aw2.help/builds/heal-alac-luminary/">&lt;p&gt;This is a very accessible build that relies on an excessive amount of healing, CC, condi cleanses and utilites, more than you will ever need. Ideally, the build should function as a low-toughness healer.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This build is low cognition, has very few repetitions and is functional in instanced content. Although the maximum APM of the build is quite high, you probably can survive without mashing keys due to how much healing is baked into the core guardian and Luminary kit. This build requires only one weapon with no requirement of a weapon swap although you must interact with the Luminary&#x27;s Forge ability.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is an excessive amount of light effects on this build and you may wish to adjust your graphics settings if the intensity is too high.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
