&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;99965&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of the Flock&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;101116&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of Febe&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: Weapon swap is optional. Alternate weapon sets should be prioritised based on utility requirements.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;
&lt;small&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: Febe gives patchy swiftness coverage but allows you to avoid swapping to staff for &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9143&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Symbol of Swiftness.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;
&lt;small&gt;&lt;em&gt;Note: If you do not use these sources of swifness, you will need to take &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9084&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Advance!&quot;.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;budget-options&quot;&gt;Budget Options&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Replace &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;24842&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Superior Rune of the Monk with &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;84171&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Superior Rune of Rebirth&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Replace &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;74326&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Superior Sigil of Transference with &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;24551&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Superior Sigil of Water&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;consumables&quot;&gt;Consumables&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;91690&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bowl of Fruit Salad with Mint Garnish OR &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;68634&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Delicious Rice Ball &lt;em&gt;(budget alternative)&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;67528&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Bountiful Maintenance Oil&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id=&quot;build&quot;&gt;Build&lt;&#x2F;h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Heal Alacrity Build&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;pre data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot; class=&quot;language-chatlink z-code&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-chatlink&quot; data-lang=&quot;chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-source z-chatlink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-begin&quot;&gt;[&amp;amp;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;DQExLS45URVhHTgBVx0tAXgdSAFWHTIBiRIAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAACMwAJAQA=&lt;span class=&quot;z-punctuation z-definition z-string z-end&quot;&gt;]&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;span&gt;&lt;&#x2F;code&gt;&lt;&#x2F;pre&gt;
&lt;hr &#x2F;&gt;
&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;skills&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;76621,77321,77300,76813,29965&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;&lt;div data-armory-embed=&#x27;specializations&#x27; data-armory-ids=&#x27;49,46,81&#x27; data-armory-49-traits=&#x27;1899,562,558&#x27; data-armory-46-traits=&#x27;624,610,612&#x27; data-armory-81-traits=&#x27;2410,2330,2368&#x27;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;div&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;trait-alternatives&quot;&gt;Trait Alternatives&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bring &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;617&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Master of Consecrations if you are taking consecrations.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;em&gt;This build is a simplified version of the heal alacrity build on &lt;a rel=&quot;noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;snowcrows.com&#x2F;builds&#x2F;raids&#x2F;guardian&#x2F;heal-alacrity-luminary-spear-staff&quot;&gt;snowcrows&lt;&#x2F;a&gt; with selective preferences for lower intensity. If you are able to adapt to the version on SC, feel free to follow their guide.&lt;&#x2F;em&gt;&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;rotation-and-utilities&quot;&gt;Rotation and Utilities&lt;&#x2F;h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The excessive amount of healing provided by this build piles on top of the already flexible healing and support capabilties of the Core Guardian kit. Of note, &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;traits&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;2394&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Light&#x27;s Gift causes &lt;strong&gt;Luminary&#x27;s Blessing&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; to heal allies whenever it is refreshed or expires.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should not be adjusting the build to try to increase healing but focus on your utilities instead.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;heal-and-alacrity-alac-rotation&quot;&gt;Heal and Alacrity Alac Rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use your virtues before &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77073&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Enter Radiant Forge&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use skills &lt;strong&gt;5-4-3-2&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; in Forge
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;to grant alacrity&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;for a strong CC&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To burst heal&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76616&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Exit Radiant Forge&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using any of your utilities will overcap on protection, which can be used on cooldown or reserved
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reserve &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76621&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Resolute Stance for Condi Cleanse and healing&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reserve &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77321&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Stalwart Stance for Aegis&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reserve &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77300&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Valorous Stance for Stability&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reserve &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76813&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Effulgent Stance for extra CC&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;29965&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Feel My Wrath!&quot; on cooldown for extra Fury uptime&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use skills &lt;strong&gt;5-4-3-2&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt; with your spear
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To grant Fury&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For a minor CC&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To burst heal&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Repeat step 1 when refreshed.&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Note: If your might uptime is patchy, consider spamming &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;78837&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Radiant Justice (F1) during your Forge rotation.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;crowd-control-rotation&quot;&gt;Crowd Control rotation&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have decent CC using only &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76978&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Brilliant Slam (Forge 5 Flip)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can extend your CC rotation by starting with &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77339&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Dazzling Hammer (Forge 2) i.e. 2-5-4-3-2&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76813&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Effulgent Stance for extra CC&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;73132&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Symbol of Luminance (Spear 5)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9128&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Sanctuary (Alt Utility Skill)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Note: More options are available but not exhausted in this guide.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;condi-cleanses&quot;&gt;Condi Cleanses&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;78604&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Radiant Resolve (F2)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;77136&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Restorative Glow (Forge 3 Flip)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;76621&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Resolute Stance (Heal)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;73094&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Solar Storm (Spear 4)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9187&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Purging Flames (Alt Utility)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9245&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Smite Condition (Alt Utility)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Note: It is very unlikely that you will require to use alternate utilities for extra condi cleanses.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&quot;situational-utilties-relics&quot;&gt;Situational Utilties&#x2F;Relics&lt;&#x2F;h4&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9251&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Wall of Reflection&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9253&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Hallowed Ground&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9153&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Stand Your Ground!&quot;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9084&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Advance!&quot; (Swiftness)&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ol&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Note: If you do not use &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9143&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Symbol of Swiftness (Staff 3) or &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;items&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;101116&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Relic of Febe, you will need alternate sources of swiftness like &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9084&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Advance!&quot;.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;small&gt;Note: &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;9084&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; &quot;Advance!&quot; has to be used on cooldown for 100% swiftness coverage but you can rely on &lt;span class=&quot;armory-inline&quot; data-armory-embed=&quot;skills&quot; data-armory-ids=&quot;78358&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;span&gt; Radiant Courage as an alternate source of Aegis.&lt;&#x2F;small&gt;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;
